snippet.textDisplay:
What an intensely deep and meaningful song. A beautiful reminder of our own insignificance in comparison to God. 
And what a magical performance! The drummer's energy and enthusiasm are contagious. Both singers compliment each other so well. Ahmed Jahanzeb's voice is like pure silk whereas Umair Jaswal's rough and deep voice is a refreshing contrast.
Thank you Coke Studio for this masterpiece. One of my all time favourites! Lots of love from Germany and UK <3
